President Jacob Zuma By Andile Mngxitama Some of you have asked that I share my views on President Zuma’s leadership and contributions, on the occasion of his 78th birthday. I then went live at 21:30 on my Facebook page to reflect on the legacy of this great leader that I’m privileged to have met and engaged with on a few occasions. Watch: https://web.facebook.com/andile.mngxi?epa=SEARCH_BOX Happy birthday Msholozi, Father of Radical Economic Transformation (RET). Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization.